snippet: Dario Franchitti and Will Power, who are first and second in the standings, will start on the ninth row. Dan Wheldon will try for $5 million from the back row.
lead_paragraph: Dario Franchitti and Will Power, who are first and second in the standings, will start on the ninth row. Dan Wheldon will try for $5 million from the back row.
